# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Sefay V1.02 — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill values
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── App ───────────────────────────────
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=3001

# ── Supabase ──────────────────────────
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key-min-32-chars

# ── Auth ──────────────────────────────
# Must be at least 32 characters random string
JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret-minimum-32-characters-here
JWT_EXPIRY=15m
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRY=7d

# ── Redis ─────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# ── Payments ──────────────────────────
# Values: stripe | mock
PAYMENT_PROVIDER=mock
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=

# ── Email ─────────────────────────────
# Leave empty to use mock mode
RESEND_API_KEY=
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@sefay.com

# ── Frontend ──────────────────────────
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000